* use_occlusion_culling (bool): Default: false.
* use_taa (bool): Default: false.
* use_xr (bool): Default: false.
* vrs_mode (VRSMode): Default: 0.
* vrs_texture (Texture2D): Default: (none).
* vrs_update_mode (VRSUpdateMode): Default: 1.
* world_2d (World2D): Default: (none).
* world_3d (World3D): Default: (none).
